{
  "stem": "16345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Auschwitz, they had a-- let's say we were in a-- in one block, which is sort of like like an army barracks.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it had cots, some three high, some four high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And those things were not too clean.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them had straw, and some of them didn't.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Some of them just had a blanket.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And during the-- during the day, this was not a work camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We only had work gangs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Like they grabbed you in the morning, throw you on a truck, you're going to work.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the day, they had also trucks patrolling the camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was like a regular street with houses, which were the barracks on both sides.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And they would-- they would ride around in a truck and grab people, threw them on the truck, beat up on them, and took them to the gas chambers.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I had-- I had a little-- a friend, who was, I think, a year or so-- at least he looked about a year or two younger than I.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I saw him thrown on the truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he jumped off the truck and started running.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they grabbed them again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They beat up on him, threw him on the truck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He jumped off the truck again.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He had more spirit than anybody I ever saw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was gassed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Occasionally they took us on work gangs.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "For instance, one time, I-- the rumor had it that some of my father's two sisters were in the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, the Germans separated the sexes very strictly.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I-- I found-- I found a way to go on a work detail to the women's camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I think we were doing some kind of plumbing or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "By the way, they-- they didn't have any real plumbing.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
